Installation:
    git clone --recursive git://github.com/Miliox/dotvim.git ~/.vim/

Create symlinks:
    ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/.gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

    or (Windows)
    mklink /H %HOME%\.vimrc %HOME%\.vim\.vimrc
    mklink /H %HOME%\.gvimrc %HOME%\.vim\.gvimrc
    mklink /J %HOME%\vimfiles %HOME%\.vim
